{"data":{"page":{"id":"9d9f00b9-ae09-5cf6-be18-9c577203a0c5","html":"<p class=\"work-links\">\n<a class=\"btn icon icon-external\" href=\"http://quizwars.herokuapp.com\" target=\"_blank\">Launch demo app</a>\n</p>\n<p>QuizWars is an R&#x26;D experiment that I did while working at SapientNitro. My aim was to learn about realtime bidirectional communication between the server and the clients.</p>\n<p>\n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 960px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 56.666666666666664%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"1\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/d3056ea9239b9afbdf0cf556e489c570/89cd4/1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d3056ea9239b9afbdf0cf556e489c570/80bba/1.jpg 500w,\n/static/d3056ea9239b9afbdf0cf556e489c570/89cd4/1.jpg 960w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  </p>\n<p>I also wanted to learn more about Node.js and sockets. I decided to use the Sails.js framework and build a quiz app. You can learn more about the project in the <a href=\"/tutorial-how-to-build-a-multi-player-quiz-app-with-sails-js/\">tutorial article</a> I wrote about it.</p>","fields":{"prefix":"30 January 2015"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Quiz Wars","cover":null}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/quizwars/","source":"work"}}